Full Description: Grant Gopher was established in 2006 to provide nonprofit organizations with up-to-date detailed information about grant programs open for application. Full Description: Prime Synthesis is the producer of Controlled Pore Glass supports for oligonucleotide synthesis. Prime Synthesis, Inc. was founded in 1988 to manufacture and sell DNA synthesis columns to support the Human Genome Project. We began development of controlled pore glass (CPG) supports, Prime Performance™ CPG, for oligo synthesis in the mid-1990s. Since then we have grown to become a key strategic partner for leading oligo therapeutic companies and oligo CMOs. In November 2016, Prime was acquired by LGC, the international life sciences and measurement company, thus complementing LGC’s existing genomics offering. Since the acquisition of Link Technologies by LGC in July 2017, we are now also combining the existing technical expertise of LINK and Prime with the Biosearch proprietary dye reagents into a single enhanced product portfolio under the banner of Nucleic Acid Chemistry.

Full Description: Tampa Homestyles Real Estate was founded to serve buyers and sellers of luxury property on the highly coveted Florida coastline. The Lead Broker is Jaime Brown, a former real estate agent with a strong background in decision and risk management. Her experience in both the corporate world and property market has made her essential in the lives of her clients.  This company has taken a personalized approach to every buyer and seller they work with. In the middle of a pandemic, it was this baseline that allowed Tampa Homestyles to quickly pivot in the face of new standards. By putting the clients' needs first, the company was able to promote new properties to buyers via virtual tours. The staff was also able to arrange for social distancing measures to ensure that relocating buyers could still see homes in person if they so chose. Jaime Brown founded the company because she noticed how her knowledge, experience, and skills could help buyers and sellers get more from every transaction. Too many deals in the industry are made without enough transparency. Buyers and sellers don't have the information they need to make better decisions for themselves, their families, and their portfolios. The website for Tampa Homestyles is packed with tips on how to increase home value, where to find a credible lender, and when it's time to close the deal. It's why people count on Tampa Homestyles Real Estate for advice on sales strategy, competitive market analysis, and risk assessment.  Jaime Brown understands the stakes of such high-value sales and works hard to achieve a fair outcome for all sides. In March, she served as the buyer's agent for a $6.4 million property on the waterfront. Her efficiency is built on metrics, and she approaches each decision with a healthy balance of caution and confidence.

Description: Mobile Software Development Company
Full Description: Appsolute Genius is a custom mobile app development firm. In late 2008, Andria Jensen and Brian Cauble were working together on software that they didn’t believe in, for a company that they no longer loved. They were looking to make a change in their own lives and a difference in the lives of others. At that time, it seemed as if everyone was buzzing about the iPhone and its quickly growing library of apps. Apple’s App Store was only a few months old, but it was already obvious that there would be endless possibilities for changing the way people use their phones. Armed with plenty of Apple devices, Andria and Brian quickly became an enthusiastic part of the Apple fan base. It was in February 2009 that our first iPhone app was created and Appsolute Genius was officially born. Our purpose would be to enhance the mobile devices people use each day, and make the lives of those who use them easier by doing so. We love making mobile devices easy, fun, and useful for people at all levels, from a tech-savvy hipster to a grandmother with her first smartphone. We love what we do, and it comes across in the services we provide. We truly believe in making products that help companies meet their goals and make their customers’ lives better. If you meet with us, you will understand our passion and excitement for the endless possibilities of mobile applications.
